cs.NA, cs.CE, cs.SE, cs.DS, cs.RO 

This paper deals with optimization and uncertainty quantification in a manufacturing process, which involves numerical simulations and modeling. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), followed by cs.CE (Computational Engineering), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.RO (Robotics).
